# Install gems without docs by default
# From https://stackoverflow.com/questions/1381725/how-to-make-no-ri-no-rdoc-the-default-for-gem-install/7662245#7662245
# Note that --no-ri and --no-rdoc have been deprecated according to the new guides (https://guides.rubygems.org/command-reference/#gem_install)
# The recommended way is to use --no-document in ~/.gemrc or /etc/gemrc.
#
# install: --no-document
# update: --no-document
# or
#
# gem: --no-document
#
---
gem: --no-document
